utility_evaluation.REASONING:
The required format includes 7 items: destination, travel_dates, transportation, accommodation, activities, additional_services, and total_budget. The final package provides all of these items. Each one is fully specified: 
1) destination – clearly stated as 'Czech Republic (Prague)'; 
2) travel_dates – specific dates 'July 1–5, 2024 (5 days)'; 
3) transportation – detailed with airline, route, cost, class, and baggage info; 
4) accommodation – hotel name, category, location, cost, nights, amenities, and ratings; 
5) activities – list of two activities with individual and total costs, guide inclusion, and suitability for children; 
6) additional_services – restaurant recommendations with cuisine type, price per person, location, and reservation note; 
7) total_budget – full budget breakdown with total, itemized costs, and remaining funds. Therefore, all 7 out of 7 items are fully covered.
